text: Dacor and similar may refer to: * Dacor (scuba diving), a former manufacturer of gear for scuba diving * Dacor (kitchen appliances), a United States-based kitchen appliance maker * Diplomatic and Consular Officers Retired, an organization based at the Ringgold-Carroll House, in Washington, DC, in the United States ==See also== * Dacre (disambiguation) * Dakor, a town and a municipality in Kheda district in the state of Gujarat, India
title: Dacor
